    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/john_carmack_775988",
        "quote": "The great games are the space sims and driving sims and these experiences where you're basically sitting at a table with nothing happening in front of you. A lot of interesting things are evolving there. There are great games that can be made.",
        "author": {
            "name": "John Carmack",
            "url": "/quotes/john_carmack_775988"
