    {
        "url": "/quotes/john_carmack_775990",
        "quote": "Oculus really started popularizing a new approach using cellphone screen technology, a wide field of view, and super-low-latency sensor tracking. It's not crappy stuff that doesn't work and makes everybody sick. When you experience Oculus technology, it's like getting religion on contact. People that try it walk out a believer.",
        "author": {
            "name": "John Carmack",
            "url": "/quotes/john_carmack_775990"
        },
        "topics": [
